  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to have a more clear action to respond to incoming requests.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Improvement\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nI would like to use a more obvious button to interact with.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"464\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-05-07 16 18 53\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/39706686-78469558-5212-11e8-8bd9-2c45a2c6ab0b.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n<img width=\"470\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-05-07 16 18 47\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/39706696-82cd274e-5212-11e8-8485-0088e3cfe3d8.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create a chat\r\n- Get a transaction request from a requester\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n-  Delete icon with arrows and animation \r\n- Add `Send` button\r\n\r\nAfter implementation of this https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/4012\r\n`Send` button should open wallet screens\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android|iOS\r\n",
